subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Josh Shipp scored 18 points and Arron Afflalo had eight of his 13 in the final nine minutes as No. 1 U.C.L.A. held off No. 6 Texas A&M on Saturday in the John R. Wooden Classic.
